                        </list>
                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; incipits of the texts; directives for
                           the ministers and the congregation (incl. the word ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡); elements of
                           the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals; some of the
                           marginal notes; most of the abbreviations; elements of the quire
                           marks.
 
 The text on fol. 4r is written alternately in crimson
                           and black lines.</seg>
                     </handNote>
